<h2>Mastering your Mac has never been easier.</h2>
<h2>Buy Now &ndash; For <span><strong>Only $29.99</strong></span></h2>
<p>Learn how to use your Mac and change your life. Feel empowered, creative and inspired.</p>
<p><img src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/7c68e66a0a1710bce433acfc3/images/51bd59e6-f436-4a86-96cb-47ca19e3d58e.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="308" align="none" /></p>
<h2>With over 100 bite-size videos covering the basics and more, you&rsquo;re going to feel empowered every time you use your Mac.</h2>
<p>Mac Clarity is an online Mac lesson video course of <strong>120+ micro lessons</strong>. You will be shown deep insights into your technology in easily digestible chunks (2-8 min videos). With over 120 videos spanning 9 levels made up of 7 hours of down to earth and empowering content you&rsquo;ll learn how to use your Mac like a Pro.</p>
<p><img src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/7c68e66a0a1710bce433acfc3/images/761219f2-85a0-4a71-a0f2-c93e69996de0.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="289" align="none" /></p>
<p>Creator Arron, starts at the very basics and talks you through each lesson step by step, with clear demonstrations so you can see where everything is as he talks about it. Learn at home at your own pace from someone who has taught this information face to face for years and knows what students want to know.</p>
<p><img src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/7c68e66a0a1710bce433acfc3/images/33b84e13-9d9e-4059-b2e1-45af729ecb05.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="413" align="none" /></p>
<p>There is also quite a focus on retraining your computing habits. Think about it, you&rsquo;ll likely be using a computer for the rest of your life, wouldn&rsquo;t it be worth getting efficient with one now rather than spending years battling away at one? As an experienced life coach Arron has shared many hints and tips on changing your habits with interactive worksheets to help you explore just a little deeper into your beliefs and relationship with your computer.</p>
<h2>Features and Highlights.</h2>
<ul>
<li>100+ micro lessons (2-8mins)</li>
<li>9 levels covering specific topics.</li>
<li>Life Coaching Tools to keep you on track and motivated.</li>
<li>Set up a Mac the way you want it</li>
<li>Have all your devices synchronized</li>
<li>Learn shortcuts to play the Mac like an instrument</li>
<li>Explore the incredible potential of iTunes</li>
<li>Simple ways to deal with your filing</li>
<li>Lot&rsquo;s of extra apps to improve your flow</li>
</ul>
